		<a href="//lens.blogs.nytimes.com/2018/01/11/exploring-the-history-of-afro-mexicans/" rel="bookmark" class="entry-title-link " title="Permanent link to Exploring the History of Afro-Mexicans"><h1 itemprop="headline" class="story-heading entry-title"><span>Exploring the History of Afro-Mexicans</span></h1></a>		<div class="story-meta entry-meta">
			<span class="author vcard byline-author"
					 itemscope=""
					 itemprop="author creator"
					 itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
					 By <span class="fn" itemprop="name">David Gonzalez</span>
				</span>			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2018-01-11T09:00:39+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">Jan. 11, 2018</time>
