			<article class="entry hentry post-149693 post type-post status-publish category-showcase tag-auschwitz-concentration-camp tag-avedon-richard tag-books-and-literature tag-budapest-hungary tag-conde-nast-publications-inc tag-faludi-susan tag-holocaust-and-the-nazi-era tag-immigration-and-emigration tag-photography tag-transgender-and-transsexuals tag-world-war-ii-1939-45 per-avedon-richard per-faludi-susan des-books-and-literature des-holocaust-and-the-nazi-era des-immigration-and-emigration des-photography des-transgender-and-transsexuals des-world-war-ii-1939-45 org-auschwitz-concentration-camp org-conde-nast-publications-inc geo-budapest-hungary news_keywords-photography" id="post-149693">
		<div class="lede lede-content">
		<div class="w480"><figure class="media slideshow promo  " id="slideshow-100000005099290" data-media-action="link-to" aria-label="media" role="group"
